  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You attempt to strike a devastating blow, launching your target into the air. Make a melee Taijutsu attack against a target in range. On a hit, that creature takes your unarmed damage as force damage, and you and they are launched 15 feet into the air for each hit landed. They must then make a Constitution Saving Throw. On a failed save, they are stunned until the end of your turn.</p><p>Until the end of your turn, you can target one affected creature with a Taijutsu Finisher regardless of range, once per turn, using either an Action or Bonus Action, ignoring its listed casting time.</p><p><strong>Empower:</strong> When you cast this Jutsu, you may expend a Ki Die. If you do, make an additional attack against the target.</p>",
